SLE12-SP5: no branching by CONFIG_PREEMPT_RT
We are missing the xmit recursion helpers 97cdcf37b57e ("net: place xmit
recursion in softnet data"). Introduce them here as we do not want to move
the recursion counter into softnet_data, that would be too intrusive and
might break kABI. Also use the helpers in all places where xmit_recursion
is accessed directly.

